OL,3,CBirmingham City Council takes Unite to
OL,4,Ccourt claiming bin workers blocked
OL,5,Cdepots
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council is taking
OL,8,FUnite the Union to court over claims
OL,9,Fthat the union has breached the terms
OL,10,Fof an existing court injunction
OL,11,Frelating to ongoing industrial action
OL,12,Fby refuse workers.
OL,14,FThe injunction, which Unite previously
OL,15,Fagreed to, prohibits the blocking of
OL,16,Fcouncil refuse collection vehicles at
OL,17,Fdepots or on city streets.
