OL,3,CBirmingham City Council takes Unite to
OL,4,Ccourt claiming bin workers blocked
OL,5,Cdepots
OL,7,FStrikes began in January after Unite
OL,8,Fsaid the Birmingham City Council told
OL,9,Fthe bin workers they would face pay
OL,10,Fcuts of up to #8,000 ` a quarter of
OL,11,Ftheir wages for some. An all-out
OL,12,Fstrike began when staff walked out on
OL,13,F11 March.
OL,15,FThe contempt of court proceedings will
OL,16,Fbe heard at the High Court in London
OL,17,Fon Monday 13 October.
