OL,3,CBirmingham City Council takes Unite to
OL,4,Ccourt claiming bin workers blocked
OL,5,Cdepots
OL,7,FAhead of the hearing, the council
OL,8,Fclaimed there has been "persistent
OL,9,Fevidence" of breaches, including
OL,10,Finstances where Unite members and
OL,11,Frepresentatives have allegedly stood
OL,12,Fin front of or leaned against moving
OL,13,Fvehicles and blocked road junctions.
OL,15,FCouncil officials say the alleged
OL,16,Factions pose serious health and safety
OL,17,Frisks to staff, protestors and the
OL,18,Fpublic, as well as causing disruption
OL,19,Fto bin collections and wider traffic.
