OL,3,CBirmingham City Council takes Unite to
OL,4,Ccourt claiming bin workers blocked
OL,5,Cdepots
OL,7,FIn a statement, the council said it
OL,8,Fsupports the right to strike and to
OL,9,Fpeaceful protest but insists the
OL,10,Finjunction requires Unite to ensure
OL,11,Fall picketing is conducted safely and
OL,12,Flawfully.
OL,14,FIt argues the situation has worsened
OL,15,Fdespite repeated warnings to the union.
OL,17,FThe council said the legal action is
OL,18,Fbeing taken "to ensure the safety of
OL,19,Four city and our workforce, including
OL,20,Fthose on strike," and to secure
OL,21,Fcompliance with the court order.
