OL,3,CBirmingham City Council takes Unite to
OL,4,Ccourt claiming bin workers blocked
OL,5,Cdepots
OL,7,FITV News Central has contacted Unite
OL,8,Fthe Union for a response.
OL,10,FIn a statement in July 2025, a Unite
OL,11,Fspokesperson said: "Unite has received
OL,12,Fnotice late today that Birmingham
OL,13,Fcouncil has applied for contempt of
OL,14,Fcourt relating to the injunction which
OL,15,Fwas issued some weeks ago.
OL,17,F"Since then, Unite has worked with our
OL,18,Fmembers and reps to ensure that there
OL,19,Fhas been compliance with the court
OL,20,Forder.
